Over its 25 years, the annual Raging Bull Awards has built a reputation in the investment industry as a unique showcase for funds and asset managers that deliver consistently superior returns for investors, as well as being a way of simply rewarding top-performing fund managers for a job well done. The February 2022 awards, for investment performance to the end of 2021, are the subject of a special edition of IOL MONEY. Delve into our free digital magazine for an "insider's" take on the best unit trust funds and fund managers in the business.